What is the area of the shaded pinwheel shown in the $5 \times 5$ grid?
{{DGM:9cd4a768406a0dae}}
$\textbf{(A)}\: 4\qquad\textbf{(B)}\: 6\qquad\textbf{(C)}\: 8\qquad\textbf{(D)}\: 10\qquad\textbf{(E)}\: 12$
